research_municipality_step.notes: Breckenridge, TX operates as a Home Rule City with a Council-Manager form of government, referring to its legislative body as the City Commission. There were some discrepancies across different sources regarding the specific individuals holding Commissioner Place 3 and Place 4. The information provided prioritizes the Texas Municipal League (TML) City Officials Directory and a recent news article from April 2025 for the most current elected officials.
